===Etymology===
Alteration of earlier {{m|en|hoise|t=to hoist}}, apparently based on the past tense forms, from {{bor|en|dum|hisen|t=to hoist}}. Compare modern {{cog|nl|hijsen|t=to hoist}}, {{cog|de|hissen|t=to hoist}}, {{cog|da|hejse|t=to hoist}}. Compare also {{cog|fr|hisser|t=to hoist}}, {{cog|it|issare|t=to hoist}}, {{cog|scn|jisari|t=to hoist}}, all borrowed from a {{etyl|gem|-}} source.

