#* {{quote-book|en|1881|H.C. Leonard|A Translation of the Anglo-Saxon Version of St. Mark’s Gospel||83|Again Pilatus answered them, What shall I do to the Jew’s king? They again cried out and said, '''Hoist''' him! Then said Pilatus, What evil did he? They so much the more cried, '''Hoist''' him!|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=zqcCAAAAQAAJ&pg=PA83}}
